annotations: - Florida Dept of Transportation (through CEI Firms) 2014-2021: I have performed nearly every capacity - Office Administrator, Project Secretary, Inspector's Aide, Resident Contracts Compliance Officer, Associate Contract Support Specialist, Contract Support Specialist in District 2 & Turnpike and as Final Estimates/Construction Area Coordinator in the District 5 FDOT for Leesburg and Oviedo Construction.
